name: TSG : Viper In Vanilla Street #2
description: Her name is Anya, Viper's girlfriend. Despite of her looks, she's actually a botanist and one of the leading expert in the study of rare plants in The Strange Gardens. That thing in her hand is one of the most sought item in all of the current known Strange Gardens, it's a mushroom spores that can only be found here in Vanilla streets. (Viper is the stranger in binary garden, Strangers are unique people picked by 'The System' to keep order in The Strange Gardens).
